About the Game
The main goal is to clear all the proposed stages, and score the highest score as possible
How to play?
^By default, use the "Right" , "Left" keys to go forward or go back,
^The "Up", "Down" keys to either jump over a ground or get to the ground below,
^The Space Key to shoot in the direction right infront of you, and if necessary move your gun up or down using the "W" and the "S" key
Pay attention to not fall into the sea... In the settings you can easily change the commands keys to be more comfortable with the game
Now you can play
GOOD LUCK !!! KILL THEM ALL !!!!
